Your snapshot endpoint is succeeding with `200 OK`, but the logs do not show any evidence that `PingUserClient.createUser(...)` is being called.

That usually means the Ping integration was added to a different method than the one used by:

```text
POST /internal/users/snapshots
```

The most likely flow is:

```text
Controller
  -> snapshot service
  -> save/update user
```

while you added the Ping call to a separate `createUser(...)` method that the snapshot flow never uses.

## 1. Add a log at the beginning of `PingUserClient.createUser`

```java
